sentences: Jeff Parker (born April 4, 1967) is an American guitarist and composer based in Los Angeles.
Parker studied at Berklee College of Music and then moved to Chicago in 1991.

Also a multi-instrumentalist, Parker has been a member of the post-rock group Tortoise since 1996, and was a founding member of Isotope 217 and the Chicago Underground Trio in the 1990s and early 2000s.
